				"text": "ArtRoll Preview — receives OSC /artroll/note <pitch> <vel> <durMs> <ksPitch> <ksHoldMs> on UDP 7474. Put this device on the edited track, BEFORE the instrument. ksPitch -1 = no keyswitch." } },
